dc_description_s: These data layers represent addresses for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NShawano_Addresses_2017.gdbN. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NShawano_Address_2017N, NShawano_Driveway_2017N, and NShawano_PrimaryStructure_2017N. [Address: Address number annotation layer. Driveway: Driveway point coverage. PrimaryStructure: Build point coverage.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
